Name: Ulrezaj
Description: Legendary Dark Archon, powerful enough to be a rival to the Dark God. It's enormous void energy can bring the entire universe to oblivion.**Can attack the ground and air**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Cost all worship energy you currentlty have and Ulrezaj will regenerate shield at 200% of that amount. At the same time, each 100 worship energy it cost will enlongate Ulrezaj's duration by 3 sec, and this effect will be doubled if it cost 500 worship energy.
Root.Name: Unification of All

Root.Tooltip: When Ulrezaj is on the battlefield, worship energy will stop to decrease and every 100 worship energy will increase Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed by 10%.
Root.Name: Will of Darkness

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's normal attack will reduce its skills CD by 1.5 sec.
Root.Name: Akashic Records

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj will automatically mind control a closest enemies within its vision and generate worship energy at 500% of its supply cost.
Root.Name: Devotion to God

Root.Tooltip: When Ulrezaj is on the battlefield, it will grant ally units 4 pts of health and shield regeneration in a large area.
Root.Name: Shelter of Void

Root.Tooltip:
When Ulrezaj leaves the battlefield, its judgement will land on all nearby enemies, dealing 750 dmg. It will also leave a mark for 30 sec at its position.
This mark will deal 20 dmg per sec to enemies within and each enemies killed inside the mark will generate 10 worship energy.
Root.Name: Judgement

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj channel immense void energy to target area and instantly destroy all enemies with target area after 2 sec (only deal 1500 to mission objectives).
Root.Name: Exile

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj will summon multiple pisonic thunders for 1.5 sec, dealing 200 dmg to all enemy units within a range of 6. Units affected by the thunders will be stunned for 5 sec and receive 40 additional dmg per sec.
Root.Name: Abyss of Thunder

Root.Tooltip: Cancel Shadow of Nifl, enable Ulrezaj to move, attack, and use other skills, and have Shadow of Nifl go into cooldown.
Root.Name: Cancel Shadow of Nifl

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj will drain the energy of a meteor, channel the void energy, and create an outburst of energy. It will deal 50 dmg to at most 3 units every 0.125 sec. Cast this skill again to cancel it.
Root.Name: Shadow of Nifl

Root.Tooltip: Ulrezaj will teleport to target location, knock back nearby enemies, and deal 100 dmg.
Root.Name: Displacement of Void

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed are increased by 10%.
Behaviors.Name: Will of Darkness

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed are increased by 20%.
Behaviors.Name: Will of Darkness

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed are increased by 30%.
Behaviors.Name: Will of Darkness

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed are increased by 40%.
Behaviors.Name: Will of Darkness

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ulrezaj's dmg and atk speed are increased by 50%.
Behaviors.Name: Will of Darkness

Behaviors.Tooltip: This unit can detect cloaked or burrowed units within its sight range.
Behaviors.Name: Detector
